ConsoleApplication - Class in mta.ads.smid.app
Console Application that can be executed in two modes: interactive mode - console application in which union/find operations can be executed using a CLI interface non-interactive mode - batch application, that loads a union instructions file an input and generates a union file output with execution statistics
this application is based on the following packages: args4j for parsing command line arguments jexl2 for parsing command line expressions
